<div id="contact-form-overlay" class="overlay hidden"></div>
<div id="contact-form-modal" class="contact-form-modal hidden">
  <button class='btn-close-modal'><i id="btn-close-modal" class="ss-delete"></i></button>
  <div class='modal-header'>
    <h4>Email</h4>
    <h3 id='company-name-1'></h3>
  </div>
  <div class='modal-body'>
    <p>Fill out the form below and <span id="company-name-2"></span> will get in touch.</p>
    <form id="contact-form" class="contact-form" action="">

      <div class='container-form-input'>
        <label for="name">First and last name</label>
        <input class='name' type="text" required pattern="[a-zA-Z0-9]+[ ][a-zA-Z0-9]+" title='e.g. John Doe'>
        <div class='checkmark'></div>
      </div>

      <div class='container-form-input container-form-input-number'>
        <label for="number">Phone number</label>
        <input class='number' id='contact-tel' type="tel" required pattern="\d{3}\d{3}\d{4}" title="e.g. 888-888-8888">
        <div class='checkmark'></div>
      </div>

      <div class='container-form-input'>
        <label for="email">Email address</label>
        <input class='email' type="email" required title='e.g. johndoe@emailprovider.com'>
        <div class='checkmark'></div>
      </div>

      <label class='label-comments' for="comments">Comments or questions</label>
      <p class='input-info'>optional</p>
      <textarea class='comments'></textarea>

      <div class='container-form-input container-form-input-ownership'>
        <p class='input-info'>optional</p>
        <label class='label-ownership' for='ownership-status'> Do you currently own a pool or spa? </label>
        <label class='label-radio'> <input type="radio" name="ownership-status" value="Yes"><span class='radio-yes'>Yes</span></label>
        <label class='label-radio'> <input type="radio" name="ownership-status" value="No"><span class='radio-no'>No</span></label>
      </div>
      <div class='button-holder'>
        <button class='btn-contact-form-submit' type='submit'>Send<span class='send-desktop-text'> my email</span></button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
  <div class='modal-footer'>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex.</p>
  </div>
</div>
